Name: Пацанский цитатник / Russian Test
About the game: Russian Test is simple test about some specific Russian culture in some places. There are 3 types of test First one is test for true russian boys from criminal areas. Second one is test about specific prison riddle Third one is mixed test ( you need complete sentence or answer for questions about films, memes and so on..) Some features - 3 types of test - Sometimes Picture can help answese the questions - Nice music Try to know something new about specific Russian culture
